<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.maxi-pedia.com/TFT+LCD+display+monitor+panel" class="external text" title="http://www.maxi-pedia.com/TFT+LCD+display+monitor+panel" rel="nofollow">What is TFT and how it works</a>, TFT LCD guide for dummies.</li>
